msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:41
#: f8659c89da4e426c9cf1429708ffe4be
msgid "Known issues"
msgstr "Problèmes connus"

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:44
#: 156d4daccc104af1aa5207b568d1b964
msgid ""
"On some graphics cards the Xfce4 Window Manager (one of the two supported "
"Dom0 Windows Managers in Qubes R2, the other being KDE) might behave "
"“strangely”, e.g. decorations might not be drawn sometimes. Also the "
"accompanying lightdm login manager might incorrectly display the wallpaper. "
"If you’re facing those problems, it’s advisable to use the KDE Window "
"Manager and kdm instead of Xfce4 and lightdm (this is default if one chooses"
" the KDE only installation option in the installer)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:46
#: a196648d3cfd4aa092f34ce06b89c67d
msgid ""
"Some icons in the Qubes Manager application might not be drawn correctly "
"when using the Xfce4 environment in Dom0. If this bothers you, please use "
"the KDE environment instead."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:48
#: adeee1c3e05040fb8fabbf3225c3ada3
msgid ""
"If your GPU is not correctly supported by the Dom0 kernel (e.g. the 3D "
"desktop effects do not run smoothly) then you might experience “heaviness” "
"with Windows 7-based AppVMs. In that case, please solve the problem with "
"your GPU support in Dom0 in the first place (by using a different kernel), "
"or install Qubes OS on a different system."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:50
#: d62eda3179a14d5b861fca76cd3d3e3f
msgid ""
"Under some circumstances, Qubes backup can create broken backup, without any"
" visible message (#902). It is advisable to verify a backup to spot the "
"problem. If you encounter this problem, backup VM directory manually."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:52
#: a35ef3c49a2b474b9c32c5b1d9d65e2b
msgid ""
"System shutdown sometimes is very slow (#903). To mitigate the problem, "
"shutdown all the VMs first."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:54
#: 1dd13a199647499698f2297e8c2af380
msgid ""
"For other known issues take a look at `our trac tickets <https://wiki.qubes-"
"os.org/query?status=accepted&status=assigned&status=new&status=reopened&type=defect&milestone=Release+2.1+(post+R2)&col=id&col=summary&col=status&col=type&col=priority&col=milestone&col=component&order=priority>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:58
#: e8ce9e8284c8461da407244c18b24e12
msgid ""
"It is advised to install updates just after system installation to apply bug"
" fixes for (some of) the above problems."
msgstr ""

