#: d2f1375286e04a7a9b853a0e28475605
msgid ""
"See :doc:`Installation Guide </user/downloading-installing-"
"upgrading/installation-guide>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:73
#: 51f4f7309db14d69be9417195f9e2bbc
msgid "Upgrading"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:77
#: bf2351b7f3484330a541a503163482fb
msgid "From Qubes R2 rc1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:80
#: 476bb2495ce141858406f63b24b7ae29
msgid ""
"Upgrading from Qubes R2 rc1 should be a simple matter of installing updates "
"for :doc:`dom0 </user/advanced-topics/how-to-install-software-in-dom0>` and "
":doc:`VMs </user/how-to-guides/how-to-install-software>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:83
#: 7eec664495354a099f3a8ae0bdf46b3b
msgid "From Qubes R2 beta 3 and older"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:86
#: 8e088ce1c76d47898f3593835d353c32
msgid ""
"The easiest and safest way to upgrade to Qubes R2 (especially from older "
"releases) is to install it from scratch and use :doc:`qubes backup and "
"restore tools </user/how-to-guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-migrate>` for "
"migrating of all of the user VMs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:88
#: 1b41327dec554f1ca15f8cc28774d372
msgid ""
"Users of R2 beta 3 can upgrade using procedure that has been described "
":doc:`here </user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/2>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:90
#: 109fefa313f24021b7bdac08b4373f6c
msgid ""
"**Note:** if the user has custom Template VMs (i.e. other than the default "
"template, e.g. created from it by cloning), or Standalone VMs, then the user"
" should perform manual upgrade from R2B3 to R2rc1, as described under the "
"link given above."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:93
#: 73b54fbcba934e3e8e00f0b3c885834b
msgid "Migrating between beta releases"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:97
#: 71e78b37838b472383a0316684f93501
msgid "From Qubes R1 to R2 beta1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:100
#: 540101efa2c4411eb31f3919e1cb7b81
msgid ""
"If you’re already running Qubes Release 1, you don’t need to reinstall, it’s"
" just enough to update the packages in your Dom0 and the template VM(s). "
"This procedure is described :doc:`here </user/downloading-installing-"
"upgrading/upgrade/2>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:103
#: 5a2e1f1dfff44d419f8c8f3b20359ccb
msgid "From Qubes R1 or R2 Beta 1 to R2 beta2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:106
#: 791f1b248088494faaef1bf7810c2a98
msgid ""
"Because of the distribution change in R2B2 (from fc13 to fc18) it’s "
"preferred that users reinstall Qubes R2B2 from scratch, and use :doc:`qubes "
"backup and restore tools </user/how-to-guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-"
"migrate>` for migrating of all of the user VMs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:108
#: 4624f14c219f45f2a2a8db97f6cf241a
msgid ""
"Advanced users (and advanced users only) can also try a manual upgrade "
"procedure that has been described :doc:`here </user/downloading-installing-"
"upgrading/upgrade/2b2>`. It’s advisable to backup your VMs before proceeding"
" anyway!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:111
#: 5521365e7c3140f0a8d698ce4025ac24
msgid "Upgrading from Qubes R1 or R2 Beta 2 to R2 beta 3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:114
#: e65856e2d87e4710921cad4cf1d009e6
msgid ""
"The easiest and safest way to upgrade to Qubes R2B3 is to install it from "
"scratch and use :doc:`qubes backup and restore tools </user/how-to-"
"guides/how-to-back-up-restore-and-migrate>` for migrating of all of the user"
" VMs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:116
#: 1353ad763d774b68b5992e26552520fe
msgid ""
"Users can also try a manual upgrade procedure that has been described "
":doc:`here </user/downloading-installing-upgrading/upgrade/2b3>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/releases/2_0/release-notes.rst:118
#: 8d469a5acd864ea787e799f0f056500f
msgid ""
"**Note:** if the user has custom Template VMs (i.e. other than the default "
"template, e.g. created from it by cloning), or Standalone VMs, then the user"
" should perform manual upgrade from R2B2 to R2B3, as described under the "
"link given above."
msgstr ""
